- post_id: dev-007
  title: I Processed 671,000 Records in 6 Minutes and 32 Seconds
  status: published
  category: data-engineering
  notes: 'Brownbook ETL pipeline. 12-step lead data processing at scale.

    Frame slots: MOMENT (BOM file breaks column parsing at 9am), SURPRISE (EF BB BF
